title: FSX - Aerosoft F-16
description:
This is the Aerosoft F-16 for FSX.



HOW TO INSTALL: (vista)
First open up C:UsersUSERNAMEAppDataLocalTemp
Then open up the installer, and select language.
Then it will come a new folder in the temp-folder you have opened.
Open that folder, and inside that folder it will be another folder, and inside that it should be a dll-file called ascrypt.dll, if not try another folder.
And then you have to open the crack-folder and replace that file with ascrypt.dll inside the temp-folder.
Then go to the installer again and next a few times, and when you comes to the registration-form, just press next without writing anything.
Press next two times, and wait for it to install.
Open up FSX and play :)
